Title: Bag Theft Investigation
Text: I’ve received a report of a bag theft near Gramados Airport. The victim, Ms. Beatrice Johnson, is waiting for me at the intersection of Comenial Street and Jorty Street, in front of the airport hotel. I should head over there and speak with her to gather more details about what happened.
CompleteText: I’ve arrived at the intersection of Comenial Street and Jorty Street. Ms. Beatrice Johnson is here, waiting for assistance. Time to speak with her and find out more about the theft.
